# Documentation on change

When you change backend, frontend, agents, vector store, Jira, or env:

1. Add one line to `docs/CHANGELOG.md` (date + short Persian summary).
2. Update the relevant section in:
   - `docs/پیاده-سازی.html` (technical detail)
   - `docs/پروژه-اصلی.html` (product/architecture)
   - `docs/شرح-پروژه-دستیار-جلسه.html` (course/RAG narrative)
   - `docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-26-meeting-assistant-design.md` (engineering spec)
3. Bump the meta date in HTML (`به‌روزرسانی ۱۴۰۵/...`) when editing those files.
4. Update root `README.md` if run commands, test counts, or stack change.

Do not leave outdated references (e.g. `data/vectors/`, `text-embedding-004`, JSON vector store).

Current stack facts: SQLite (`data/meetings.db`), ChromaDB (`data/chroma/`), `gemini-embedding-001`, smart RAG (small-talk skip), Jira issues in English, Astro SSR meeting page, 93 unit + 8 live tests.
